<biogHist>
<abstract>Halls Creek Mission was run by the Australian Inland Mission from 1943. Children at the Mission were under the guardianship of the heads of the departments responsible for Aboriginal welfare. In 1955, some people from Moola Bulla Station moved the Mission when the Station closed. Halls Creek Mission closed in 1960.</abstract>
<p>Halls Creek Mission was converted to the government-run Charles Perkins Hostel by 1962.</p>
